#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:1
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:3
msgid ""
"To quickly start the simulation, you can use the following code snippet to "
"run a simulation for a robot in a world."
msgstr "创建一个 Python 文件并复制下面的代码片段即可运行仿真。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:5
msgid ""
"Create a Python file and copy the following code snippet to run the "
"simulation."
msgstr "创建一个 Python 文件并复制下面的代码片段即可运行仿真。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:23
msgid ""
"Create a configuration YAML file *robot_world.yaml* and copy the following "
"configuration to the file."
msgstr "创建配置文件 *robot_world.yaml*，并将以下配置复制到该文件中。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:25
msgid ""
"All the configurations are set in the YAML file. You can change the "
"configurations in the YAML file to customize the simulation. The following "
"is an example of the configuration file *robot_world.yaml*."
msgstr "所有配置都写在该 YAML 文件中，你可以通过修改这些配置来自定义仿真。下面是 *robot_world.yaml* 的示例。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:44
msgid ""
"Run the script and a window opens showing the differential-drive robot "
"navigating from its start to the goal:"
msgstr "运行脚本后会弹出一个窗口，显示差速驱动机器人从起点导航到目标："

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:46
msgid ""
"Quick-start simulation — a differential-drive robot navigating to its goal"
msgstr "快速开始仿真 —— 差速驱动机器人导航到目标"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:52
msgid "Next steps"
msgstr "后续步骤"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:54
msgid ""
"[Make Environment](../usage/make_environment.md) — the simulation loop, "
"status control, and dynamic objects in depth."
msgstr ""
"[Make Environment](../usage/make_environment.md) —— 深入了解仿真循环、状态控制和动态对象。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:55
msgid ""
"[Configure robots and obstacles](../usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md) — "
"kinematics, shapes, and multi-object scenes."
msgstr ""
"[Configure robots and obstacles](../usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md) —— "
"运动学、形状和多对象场景。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:56
msgid ""
"[YAML Configuration](../yaml_config/configuration.md) — the full "
"configuration reference with an interactive schema explorer."
msgstr ""
"[YAML Configuration](../yaml_config/configuration.md) —— 完整的配置参考，附带交互式 "
"schema 浏览器。"

